<h4 class="widget-title widgettitle">Child Find and Grand Blanc Academy Child Find Procedures</h4>
			<div class="textwidget">
<p> </p>
<p>Child Find is a program of active outreach by the Michigan Department of Education, Genesee Intermediate School District, and local school districts.  Child Find specifically requires the district to identify, locate, and evaluate all children with disabilities, birth through age twenty-five.</p>
